    <h1 class="page__title">Annual Seminars</h1>
    <p>MapBiomas products are developed under constant evolution. Each year a new collection of land cover and land use maps is launched, improving and extending the period. The launches occured in the 1st Technical Seminar and 1st, 2nd and 3rd Annual Seminars of MapBiomas, where there were discussions with external invited participants about the collections and perspectives of land use monitoring and its applications in Brazil.</p>

    <hr />

    <h2 class="page__subtitle">3rd MapBiomas Annual Seminar - Collection 3</h2>
